<%= render "hero" %>
<div class="container">
    <div class="about">
        <div class='about-text'>
            <h1>Your work speaks for itself. <br> We just help spread the word online.</h1>
            <p>We're a small digital agency located in Boone, NC, that specializes in designing and developing professional, modern, 
            websites at fair prices.  We exist to fill the gap between large, expensive, digital agencies and small shops who may not have
            the design and development skills you need.</p>    
        </div>
        <div class="blog-latest">
            <% if @post.nil? %>
            <% else %>
                <h2>Latest Blog:</h2>
                <h3><%= @post.title %> | <%= "#{@post.created_at.strftime("%b %e, %Y")}" %></h3>
                <div id="blog-body">
                    <%= raw(@post.body.truncate(300)) %>   <%= link_to 'read more', posts_path %>
                </div>
            <% end %>
        </div>
        <%= link_to contact_path do %>
        <div class="contact-bubble">
            <i class="fa fa-phone" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-envelope" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>
        <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="features">
        <div class="feature" id="feature-1">
            <div class="feature-image">
                <%= image_tag('seo') %>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
                <h2>SEO on every page</h2>
                <p>Proper code and design matters.  Search engines rank websites 
                coded in industry standard formats higher than poorly coded sites.  
                From headings, to “alt” captions on photos, we’ll do the work behind 
                the scenes to make sure your website is given the best shot at a higher 
                ranking.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature" id="feature-2">
            <div class="feature-image">
                <%= image_tag('design') %>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
                <h2>Truly custom design</h2>
                <p>We design each of our websites from scratch to meet your unique 
                business’ needs and your customer’s expectations.  We'll never force
                you to choose between a pre-made template that may or may not be a 
                good fit for your vision.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature" id="feature-3">
            <div class="feature-image">
                <%= image_tag('real_turf_gallery') %>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
                <h2>Dynamic features</h2>
                <p>Dynamic fading and sliding, scrollable and sortable image galleries, and
                other responsive features ensure your prospective customer has a great first
                experience with your company.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature" id="feature-4">
            <div class="feature-image">
                <%= image_tag('design') %>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
                <h2>Google analytics tracking</h2>
                <p>Data drives decision-making.  With analytics built-in, you'll know
                what pages client's like, how long they stay on your page, and whether
                your online marketing efforts are actually leading people to your site.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature" id="feature-5">
            <div class="feature-image">
                <%= image_tag('admin_view') %>    
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
                <h2>Easily update content</h2>
                <p>We offer custom CRM packages for our client's who need to update their own
                content.  Add and update blog posts, testimonials, special offers, pricing, 
                and gallery images with ease, all without hiring a web management company.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
